{"tid":1745580,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【細價股洗倉】HMVOD突然急挫八成 蕭定一間接持有權益","createTime":"2019-11-22T09:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:50:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdd5508dfb08f885cfe66a2a01cab7f063106ab","tid":1745580,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"近日有細價股連日急挫，HMVOD（8103）午後股價突然急挫八成，低見0.35元，最新下跌77.8%，報0.4元，成交額1.59億元，市值只剩5,680萬元。<br />\nHMVOD由前稱HMV數碼中國的中國創意數碼娛樂（8078）持股29%，目前後者市值只得2,683萬元，而中創數碼主席蕭定一最新持股為8.22%，市值僅220萬元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191122/large/1574405506_bb76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191122%2Flarge%2F1574405506_bb76.jpg&h=37148091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191122/60296225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F60296225&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=24399c68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191122%2F60296225&h=d135626f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191122/60296225</a>"},{"pid":"3618cec7bb0d27a72c9623795d9c4aa5c902b9ed","tid":1745580,"uid":4258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"8字頭殼唔值錢"},{"pid":"ef4eba82469bc15a65af834a384868e739de3451","tid":1745580,"uid":286412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:50:51.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你好我係拍片嘅本人，有冇人知道個手足點樣？可以幫手retweet 比多啲人睇到,想推到出國際俾記者報道同有冇人知道有咩方法可以 ？謝謝 Twitter link <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https:/